snippet.textDisplay:
I don’t know why this song made me so emotional. Maybe it’s because I just graduated and I’m struggling with colleges, scared of the future and not feeling good enough (and a classroom reminds me just that) BUT JUST WANTED TO SAY: I love you so much Stay,
Even though I personally don’t know many of you, I know we are a family and that means a lot to me. Thank you for supporting our boys.

Some of you may be going through hard times rn and I can’t do much but remember that times really do come and go, I say this from experience, so hang in there because I (lee) KNOW that you can do it! You are never alone in this family

also I love you so much Stray Kids
